Register - Create user
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register Content-Type: application/json

{ "username": "alice", "password": "secret", "name": "Alice" }

Login - Get token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login Content-Type: application/json

{ "username": "alice", "password": "secret" }

Who am I - /auth/me
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

Create Stream
POST {{baseUrl}}/streams Content-Type: application/json Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{ "title": "Live de Games", "summary": "Gameplay e bate-papo", "url": "https://example.com/stream.m3u8", "tags": ["games","live"] }

List / Search Streams
GET {{baseUrl}}/streams?q=games&page=1&limit=10

Get Stream by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/streams/{{streamId}}

Update Stream (owner only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/streams/{{streamId}} Content-Type: application/json Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{ "title": "Live de Games (Atualizado)", "summary": "Resumo atualizado", "tags": ["games","highlights"] }

Delete Stream (owner only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/streams/{{streamId}} Authorization: Bearer {{token}}